Class Coordinates

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.geom.Point2D
      • java.awt.Point
        • mangan.Coordinates
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Coordinates
extends java.awt.Point
    Own class created to handle all the information of every single robot. A set of operators allow us to add coordinates or velocity, substract, get the components, etc.
    See Also:
